006.","meanings":["1  Sanskrit: a term of endearment, ‘darling boy’.","2  Prakrit: ‘king’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Hugues lll De Broyes was born in 1125, in Broyes, Oise, Hauts-de-France, France. He had at least 1 son and 2 daughters with Stéphanie De Bar-le-Duc. He died in 1199, in his hometown, at the age of 74."},"et":{"1125–1199":"1125–1199","1125–1178":"1125–1178","1145–1208":"1145–1208","1149–Female":"1149–Surnud","1155–Female":"1155–Surnud","1149":"1149","1125":"1125","1145":"1145","Abt 1155":"umbes 1155","1178":"1178","1199":"1199","1155":"1155","ABT 1149":"umbes 1149","1208":"1208","12 March 1178":"12. märts 1178","Broyes, Oise, Picardie, France":"Broyes, Oise, Picardie, Prantsusmaa","of,Broyes,Marne,France":"Broyes, Marne, Champagne-Ardenne, Prantsusmaa","France":"Prantsusmaa","Broyes, Oise, Hauts-de-France, France":"Broyes, Oise, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1125–1199":"1125–1199","1125–1178":"1125–1178","1145–1208":"1145–1208","1149–Female":"1149–Kuollut","1155–Female":"1155–Kuollut","1149":"1149","1125":"1125","1145":"1145","Abt 1155":"noin 1155","1178":"1178","1199":"1199","1155":"1155","ABT 1149":"noin 1149","1208":"1208","12 March 1178":"12. maaliskuuta 1178","Broyes, Oise, Picardie, France":"Broyes, Oise, Picardie, Ranska","of,Broyes,Marne,France":"Broyes, Marne, Champagne-Ardenne, Ranska","France":"Ranska","Broyes, Oise, Hauts-de-France, France":"Broyes, Oise, Hauts-de-France, Ranska"},"fr":{"1125–1199":"1125–1199","1125–1178":"1125–1178","1145–1208":"1145–1208","1149–Female":"1149–Décédée","1155–Female":"1155–Décédée","1149":"1149","1125":"1125","1145":"1145","Abt 1155":"environ 1155","1178":"1178","1199":"1199","1155":"1155","ABT 1149":"environ 1149","1208":"1208","12 March 1178":"12 mars 1178","Broyes, Oise, Picardie, France":"Broyes, Oise, Picardie, France","of,Broyes,Marne,France":"Broyes, Marne, Champagne-Ardenne, France","France":"France","Broyes, Oise, Hauts-de-France, France":"Broyes, Oise, Hauts-de-France, France","lifeS